{"type": "article", "id": 38998, "title": "这个便签条，想在你的书里藏一只海怪｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-20T23:18:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 38137, "name": "Banale"}, {"id": 38716, "name": "Re+g"}, {"id": 38717, "name": "Naver Labs"}, {"id": 38718, "name": "Public Group"}, {"id": 37178, "name": "Don Moyer"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 100, "image": "img/article/article_show/201703210711502YGdwoV0O7XvyRpk.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>TACO-ASHI by Re+g</h3><p>只要变个造型，平时不起眼的便签条也能给日常生活注入一些意想不到的乐趣。日本设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.replug.jp/\">Re+g</a> 最近就推出了一款以章鱼为造型的 TACO-ASHI 便签条，它的头部和八条腿都可以扯下进行创作。粘贴得当的话，别人或许还会以为你在书里藏了一只红色的海怪。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.replug.jp/fs/replug/c/taco\">购买链接</a>，售价为 880 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215735jNUGnqOipWLaMhVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215735uP1Ek2TKLg7ht5iH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215737hYsZxdEw8e2BSqiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215736wSoi4GYt3a8nOKIg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215735Q3fh60xJkuNSMnAs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Omnivore Bowls by Don Moyer</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/37286.html\">青花瓷盘里藏着外星人</a>的 <a href=\"http://calamityware.com/\">Calamityware</a> 系列吗？在完成了瓷盘的众筹之后，来自美国匹茨堡的 Don Moyer 又带来了以杂食动物为主题的四只青花瓷碗。无论是碗底的“厨房大爆炸”还是外围那几只拟人化动物大厨，都延续了那种带有冷幽默的反差感。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/159974695/omnivore-bowls\">链接</a>参与众筹，一套的价格为 56 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703202158007PSg5ALyl2RUuxZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215800T0vemNr7s9FjWAJV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215924WARhqYcSH34eGUzd.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.601471\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Silver Mask by Banale</h3><p>为了让口罩能够提供更全面的防护，意大利设计品牌 <a href=\"http://banale.com/\">Banale</a> 推出了一款利用涂银外层增强抗菌功效的口罩 Silver Mask。多层结构的口罩配有运动、通勤和污染三种不同过滤级别的滤芯，可以满足不同地区的使用需要，在每天使用的情况下需要每月更换一次。它的佩戴系统也相当特别，具有夜光效果的系绳可以在头戴和耳戴式之间轻松切换。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1423851799/silver-mask-high-performance-high-fashion-breathin\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 29 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215822uJz5ItBYi8Kax7Vq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584683\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215825cK0AUDlkaIvwYNBQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703202158225wEeFOGZ9dRf72oT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.410294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215825AR4gKzsO7tbTX5Q3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Gravity by Naver Labs</h3><p>“重力”是不少设计师希望挑战的主题，最近来自韩国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.naverlabs.com/\">Naver Labs</a> 的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/kyuminha\">Kyumin Ha</a> 带来了这款名为 Gravity 概念耳机，它可以在没有外部支撑的状态下与桌面保持 45 度角的直立状态，像是一件桌面装饰品。佩戴时 Gravity 依然处于倾斜状态，可以有效地减轻头戴式耳机带来的压迫感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215847xViSbt7znfHDdJ36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703202158474xQXJSdvy5lM2uGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.764059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215847XQWV74GMF0gukjiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680929\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215846nu7eC5hXYtgBMbsJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.092910\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>SML Milk by Public Group</h3><p>这款名为 SML 的牛奶概念包装是白俄罗斯创意机构 <a href=\"http://www.pgr.by/\">Public Group</a> 的作品，设计师以服饰所采用的三种大小为灵感，辅以不同配色以及纸盒上由小到大的凸点来表示牛奶的脂肪含量，看起来既直观又富有趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215910b2ko9Z3YxhMWNtj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215910KyN8G6rYkhFaQBqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215910YN6XijGOkchoyfC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215910V57k0sFNv8znpDyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320215910Z1IBTLXPlO04mNJS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Glass Sculptures by Yuki Tsunoda</h3><p>自 2012 年起，日本艺术家<a href=\"http://www.tunodayuki02.com/\">角田夕贵</a>就开始以各类昆虫为原型制作还原度极高的玻璃雕塑，希望人们能够感受到这些小生物特有的美丽。由于昆虫的尺寸都非常迷你，角田在制作时需要用针和刀片等同样小一号的工具耐心地为每一个部位塑形。如果你喜欢这些玻璃雕塑，可以通过她的<a href=\"https://glassinsetto.shopselect.net/\">网店</a>购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703202200439ld6w8mbhO02opsk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320220043IfTvnHFatujpJkqR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320220043zX7F6D1ly2BeNP50.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170320220044sNMmwO3HraDJUgTh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703202200443tIcpHOChiTAyaqj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}